<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@accepts(gint, Clutter.ModelSortFunc, gpointer, GLib.DestroyNotify)
@returns(none)
def set_sort(column, func, user_data, notify)
</code></synopsis>
<p>Sorts @model using the given sorting function.</p>

<table>
<tr>
<td><p>column :</p></td>
<td><p>the column to sort on</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><p>func :</p></td>
